title: WFRP 1st Edition Character Pack (restored)
description:
Warhammer Fantasy Roleplay 1st Edition Character Pack (restored)
================================================================

Format: PDF of scanned pages
Language: English
First Published: 1987
Publisher: Games Workshop

Character Pack for WFRP 1st Edition with expanded information for character creation.

I have done a bit of restoration on an existing scan to straighten pages and include missing bits.

This is the first version of the Character Pack by Games Workshop. If anyone has the second version by Flame Publications ( yellow cover ) then please post a comment below to help in getting a PDF version out there.
